1
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:16,632
When I first met Sister Ling'er,

2
00:00:16,933 --> 00:00:17,766
I already knew

3
00:00:17,833 --> 00:00:19,499
she was destined for greatness.

4
00:00:19,500 --> 00:00:20,500
Hindsight hero.

5
00:00:30,900 --> 00:00:32,466
Could this be Ling'er's Spirit Phase?

6
00:00:40,367 --> 00:00:42,999
No matter who you are,

7
00:00:43,567 --> 00:00:46,432
today this lord will slay gods
if they stand in my way—

8
00:00:46,567 --> 00:00:48,966
and Buddhas too.

9
00:01:21,900 --> 00:01:24,366
Anyone who dares hinder the Holy Sect's plans

10
00:01:24,700 --> 00:01:27,599
will be crushed to dust!

11
00:01:33,733 --> 00:01:34,999
How am I flying?

12
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:37,532
Bro, I'm right here!

13
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:39,400
Ling'er!

14
00:01:40,600 --> 00:01:41,866
First level of the Demon-Subduing Curse—

15
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,200
Thunder envelops me!

16
00:01:44,300 --> 00:01:44,699
Brother Hu!

17
00:01:45,133 --> 00:01:46,133
I'll leave this to you.

18
00:01:46,233 --> 00:01:47,532
Don't worry, I can hold them off.

19
00:01:47,533 --> 00:01:48,199
And me too!

20
00:01:48,300 --> 00:01:49,899
Go beat the crap out of that perverted sect!

21
00:01:51,500 --> 00:01:53,599
The All-Heavens Demon-Subduing Array has been broken.

22
00:01:54,633 --> 00:01:56,632
The Great Wilderness is on the brink of destruction.

23
00:01:57,500 --> 00:01:59,499
You're just a useless Phase-less person.

24
00:02:00,300 --> 00:02:02,999
Why fight against heaven?

25
00:02:20,300 --> 00:02:20,732
Ling'er!

26
00:02:21,200 --> 00:02:22,200
Circulate your Phase power.

27
00:02:22,300 --> 00:02:23,300
Feel your Spirit Phase.

28
00:02:23,700 --> 00:02:25,499
Even if you save the Great Wilderness,

29
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:27,666
when the Heavenly Tribulation comes
and the evil god descends...

30
00:02:27,733 --> 00:02:30,766
it will only turn more people to ash.

31
00:02:31,300 --> 00:02:32,399
Heavenly Tribulation...

32
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,066
Evil god...

33
00:02:33,100 --> 00:02:34,832
Neither is an excuse for you to kill!

34
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:35,732
Second Phase Technique!

35
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,832
Spirit Source Limit Break!

36
00:02:38,100 --> 00:02:39,566
Foolish and stubborn.

37
00:02:39,600 --> 00:02:41,532
Die!

38
00:02:45,100 --> 00:02:47,266
Form without restraint.

39
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:50,366
Illusion born from the heart.

40
00:02:50,700 --> 00:02:53,032
Transcending life and death.

41
00:02:53,600 --> 00:02:56,832
Freedom without limit!

42
00:02:57,900 --> 00:03:00,466
Soul-Devouring Annihilation!

43
00:03:01,233 --> 00:03:02,233
Ling'er!

44
00:03:09,100 --> 00:03:09,532
Stay back!

45
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,166
I'll handle this tentacle freak.

46
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,800
Secret Technique—

47
00:03:12,933 --> 00:03:14,099
Ice Seals the Nine Provinces!

48
00:03:26,733 --> 00:03:27,733
Mu Xue!

49
00:03:30,700 --> 00:03:31,700
Are you alright?

50
00:03:32,500 --> 00:03:33,500
You're too foolish.

51
00:03:36,033 --> 00:03:37,366
You insignificant ants!

52
00:03:37,633 --> 00:03:40,132
To sacrifice yourselves for the Holy Sect
is already a great honor.

53
00:03:40,433 --> 00:03:41,832
Yet you dare resist!

54
00:03:42,033 --> 00:03:43,532
Death is too merciful for you.

55
00:04:02,933 --> 00:04:03,933
Three-Headed Flood Dragon...

56
00:04:04,833 --> 00:04:05,833
Rest in peace.

57
00:04:11,133 --> 00:04:11,699
Oh no!

58
00:04:12,000 --> 00:04:13,000
It's absorbing the evil mist!

59
00:04:13,433 --> 00:04:14,433
Merging with all that spirit evil...

60
00:04:17,500 --> 00:04:18,332
Ding Xiao!

61
00:04:18,500 --> 00:04:21,066
Everyone will die because of you!

62
00:04:32,800 --> 00:04:35,166
This young master is going all out today!

63
00:04:47,567 --> 00:04:50,199
Mere Ninth Star Spirit Adept Realm...

64
00:04:50,467 --> 00:04:53,032
Nothing but a worthless nobody.

65
00:05:06,933 --> 00:05:07,966
Brother can't hold on much longer!

66
00:05:10,467 --> 00:05:11,766
Why struggle?

67
00:05:12,467 --> 00:05:14,266
Death is inevitable either way.

68
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:16,266
Stop wasting your energy.

69
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:21,332
If I can isolate the evil qi...

70
00:05:21,733 --> 00:05:22,866
and those spirit evils...

71
00:05:28,833 --> 00:05:29,366
Phase Technique!

72
00:05:29,700 --> 00:05:30,700
Phase Evil Returns to Origin!

73
00:05:38,833 --> 00:05:40,299
How is this possible?!

74
00:05:40,323 --> 00:06:13,923
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

75
00:06:15,233 --> 00:06:16,666
We need to repair the grand array first.

76
00:06:16,767 --> 00:06:17,767
It won't hold much longer!

77
00:06:22,767 --> 00:06:23,767
Little Broken Ball!

78
00:06:24,433 --> 00:06:26,166
Little Broken Ball, are you still there?

79
00:06:33,767 --> 00:06:34,999
The grand array has fallen.

80
00:06:35,567 --> 00:06:37,266
Heaven itself wants me dead.

81
00:06:37,633 --> 00:06:40,266
This is not a defeat by force...

82
00:06:40,900 --> 00:06:41,832
This time, the Great Wilderness

83
00:06:41,833 --> 00:06:43,099
is doomed.

84
00:06:47,200 --> 00:06:47,466
AR

85
00:06:57,533 --> 00:06:58,533
Xia dogs!

86
00:06:58,633 --> 00:06:59,532
Invading our lands...

87
00:06:59,633 --> 00:07:00,666
must be exterminated!

88
00:07:01,267 --> 00:07:01,966
Mother...

89
00:07:02,100 --> 00:07:03,266
Forgive your unfilial son.

90
00:07:03,333 --> 00:07:04,566
I'll serve you again in the next life.

91
00:07:04,567 --> 00:07:05,567
Dream Sister...

92
00:07:05,700 --> 00:07:06,700
Don't wait for me.

93
00:07:06,833 --> 00:07:08,166
Find a good family.

94
00:07:08,167 --> 00:07:09,499
Father has broken his promise.

95
00:07:09,700 --> 00:07:11,266
You must honor and care for Mother.

96
00:07:11,267 --> 00:07:12,399
Help me look after our parents.

97
00:07:12,400 --> 00:07:14,066
I can feel their pain...

98
00:07:14,333 --> 00:07:15,832
as if trapped in the deepest hell,

99
00:07:16,100 --> 00:07:17,166
unable to transcend.

100
00:07:17,400 --> 00:07:19,632
At that time, the Heavenly Venerable
who saves from suffering

101
00:07:19,900 --> 00:07:21,632
shall fill the ten directions of the world.

102
00:07:22,200 --> 00:07:23,732
With your mighty divine power,

103
00:07:24,133 --> 00:07:26,099
you rescue all sentient beings,

104
00:07:26,367 --> 00:07:28,199
leading them away from delusion.

105
00:07:28,467 --> 00:07:30,466
Yet sentient beings remain unaware,

106
00:07:30,967 --> 00:07:33,166
like the blind beholding the sun and moon.

107
00:07:36,367 --> 00:07:37,367
Grandpa...

108
00:07:37,533 --> 00:07:38,566
Ah Xiao...

109
00:07:39,100 --> 00:07:41,166
All these years, curing Ling'er

110
00:07:41,333 --> 00:07:42,566
has been so hard on you.

111
00:07:42,767 --> 00:07:43,932
You've suffered greatly.

112
00:07:44,100 --> 00:07:44,632
Grandpa...

113
00:07:45,667 --> 00:07:47,066
This is all my fault.

114
00:07:48,367 --> 00:07:49,899
I shouldn't have rashly opened the grand array.

115
00:07:52,133 --> 00:07:53,766
Everything is fated.

116
00:07:54,167 --> 00:07:56,166
Do not let it disturb your Dao heart.

117
00:07:58,067 --> 00:07:59,067
Grandpa...

118
00:07:59,600 --> 00:08:00,600
What should I do?

119
00:08:02,333 --> 00:08:03,499
Ten years ago,

120
00:08:03,733 --> 00:08:06,999
I led over a thousand Spirit Phase masters
into the Great Wilderness to eradicate evil.

121
00:08:07,200 --> 00:08:08,532
Nearly all perished.

122
00:08:08,867 --> 00:08:10,132
Leaving behind hidden dangers.

123
00:08:10,467 --> 00:08:11,866
This All-Heavens Demon-Subduing Array

124
00:08:12,000 --> 00:08:13,599
may seem to protect the Great Wilderness,

125
00:08:13,767 --> 00:08:15,599
but in truth, it also imprisons it.

126
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:17,432
Do you still remember your great vow?

127
00:08:19,633 --> 00:08:20,633
To redeem all evil spirits,

128
00:08:20,967 --> 00:08:21,967
and bring salvation to every living being.

129
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:27,432
Grandpa...

130
00:08:27,633 --> 00:08:28,566
This unfinished path...

131
00:08:29,667 --> 00:08:30,799
I will walk it in your stead.

132
00:08:30,933 --> 00:08:31,599
Mm.

133
00:08:36,000 --> 00:08:37,266
As a disciple of the Gui Division,

134
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:39,766
I will always remember:
salvation before slaughter.

135
00:08:41,033 --> 00:08:41,566
I offer the power of our ancestors.

136
00:08:41,567 --> 00:08:42,566
I offer the power of our ancestors.

137
00:08:42,967 --> 00:08:43,832
With this vow's strength,

138
00:08:44,700 --> 00:08:46,266
I shall redeem these countless wronged souls!

139
00:08:52,733 --> 00:08:53,766
If we live, we live together.

140
00:08:54,667 --> 00:08:56,699
If we die, we die together.

141
00:08:57,533 --> 00:08:58,533
Mm.

142
00:08:59,400 --> 00:09:00,499
Phase Evil Returns to Origin!

143
00:09:11,967 --> 00:09:13,366
The living are but passing travelers,

144
00:09:13,800 --> 00:09:15,032
the dead are those returning home.

145
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,366
Heaven and earth are one fleeting inn,

146
00:09:16,533 --> 00:09:17,699
sharing the same eternal sorrow of dust.

147
00:09:39,067 --> 00:09:40,067
Grandpa...

148
00:09:40,567 --> 00:09:41,599
Ling'er misses you so much.

149
00:09:42,700 --> 00:09:43,832
Silly child.

150
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:45,966
Grandpa will become a star in the sky

151
00:09:46,700 --> 00:09:48,799
and watch over you all.

152
00:09:54,800 --> 00:09:55,266
Grandpa...

153
00:09:56,833 --> 00:09:57,399
Don't go!

154
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:16,432
We won!

155
00:10:16,433 --> 00:10:21,599
We won! We actually won!

156
00:10:21,933 --> 00:10:23,599
Just as that saying foretold.

157
00:10:25,400 --> 00:10:26,400
But Senior Brother Yuan...

158
00:10:27,333 --> 00:10:28,666
With such fine juniors,

159
00:10:29,433 --> 00:10:30,432
you can rest without regrets.

160
00:10:36,767 --> 00:10:38,366
It feels like waking from a nightmare.

161
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,200
Finally awake.

162
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,000
The evil mist has vanished.

163
00:10:42,333 --> 00:10:45,032
The people here no longer have to live in hiding.

164
00:10:45,033 --> 00:10:45,566
Mm.

165
00:10:48,233 --> 00:10:48,699
Ling'er...

166
00:10:48,867 --> 00:10:49,867
Your abnormal Phase...

167
00:10:50,033 --> 00:10:50,599
It's gone.

168
00:10:50,900 --> 00:10:51,366
It's gone.

169
00:10:51,900 --> 00:10:53,632
I'll never be tormented by that monster again.

170
00:10:54,100 --> 00:10:55,966
I still need to train hard and protect everyone.

171
00:10:57,433 --> 00:10:57,999
Good.

172
00:10:58,567 --> 00:10:59,499
Come with me to the Wu Xuan Sect.

173
00:10:59,967 --> 00:11:01,499
I'll personally oversee your rigorous training.

174
00:11:01,833 --> 00:11:02,833
Mm.

175
00:11:04,533 --> 00:11:05,099
Princess...

176
00:11:05,433 --> 00:11:06,532
Using secret arts like that

177
00:11:06,967 --> 00:11:08,632
could cost you your life and destroy your Dao.

178
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:10,366
Mu Xue...

179
00:11:10,600 --> 00:11:11,266
Are you alright?

180
00:11:13,433 --> 00:11:13,899
Don't worry.

181
00:11:14,367 --> 00:11:15,132
With my master here,

182
00:11:15,367 --> 00:11:16,399
I'll be back to full strength in a few days.

183
00:11:18,367 --> 00:11:19,367
This Phantom Scale Jade of the South Sea.

184
00:11:19,867 --> 00:11:21,132
will help you break through to the Spirit Martial Realm.

185
00:11:21,533 --> 00:11:22,266
Keep it safe.

186
00:11:22,267 --> 00:11:22,532
This...

187
00:11:23,133 --> 00:11:23,832
I can't accept a reward without merit.

188
00:11:24,900 --> 00:11:25,799
Take it.

189
00:11:26,267 --> 00:11:27,099
That's an order.

190
00:11:28,500 --> 00:11:29,199
These past days...

191
00:11:29,300 --> 00:11:30,966
Thank you, Princess Mu Xue,
for all your invaluable help.

192
00:11:31,333 --> 00:11:31,932
I'm truly grateful.

193
00:11:32,500 --> 00:11:34,199
H-How did you know?

194
00:11:35,400 --> 00:11:36,400
I just do.

195
00:11:36,900 --> 00:11:37,900
Then...

196
00:11:38,433 --> 00:11:39,599
Since you've met this princess,

197
00:11:39,833 --> 00:11:40,732
why haven't you paid your respects?

198
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:41,466
You...

199
00:11:41,833 --> 00:11:42,833
Your attitude changes faster than flipping a book.

200
00:11:43,767 --> 00:11:44,366
Just kidding.

201
00:11:45,333 --> 00:11:46,532
I've had enough training in the Great Wilderness.

202
00:11:46,967 --> 00:11:48,332
Master, let's head back.

203
00:11:48,500 --> 00:11:49,299
There will be plenty of time ahead.

204
00:11:50,133 --> 00:11:51,133
Until we meet again.

205
00:11:51,667 --> 00:11:54,032
You haven't fallen for that silly boy, have you?

206
00:11:54,500 --> 00:11:55,266
Master!

207
00:11:55,433 --> 00:11:56,433
What nonsense are you saying?

208
00:11:56,800 --> 00:11:57,899
We're just friends.

209
00:12:00,100 --> 00:12:00,832
Brother Ding Xiao.

210
00:12:01,267 --> 00:12:02,466
What are your plans moving forward?

211
00:12:04,167 --> 00:12:05,432
The Great Wilderness has been reborn.

212
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:07,699
Those laws of the jungle,

213
00:12:08,333 --> 00:12:09,666
where the weak are prey to the strong,

214
00:12:10,400 --> 00:12:11,466
should vanish along with the evil mist.

215
00:12:11,900 --> 00:12:12,966
I want to work with the Wu Xuan Sect

216
00:12:13,733 --> 00:12:15,966
to build a Great Wilderness City,

217
00:12:17,133 --> 00:12:18,232
a safe haven for all the displaced villagers.

218
00:12:18,800 --> 00:12:19,432
It sounds impossible.

219
00:12:19,600 --> 00:12:20,299
But how will we know

220
00:12:21,367 --> 00:12:22,367
if we don't try?

221
00:12:22,600 --> 00:12:24,232
Well said.

222
00:12:24,600 --> 00:12:25,600
Leave the sect matters to me and Master.

223
00:12:25,967 --> 00:12:27,766
You can rest assured.

224
00:12:27,767 --> 00:12:28,632
When I first met you, Brother Ding Xiao,

225
00:12:28,633 --> 00:12:30,899
I already knew you were no ordinary person.

226
00:12:31,167 --> 00:12:31,432
Good.

227
00:12:31,833 --> 00:12:32,899
I'll rally the Thunder Leopard Village

228
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:34,466
to be the first to join Great Wilderness City.

229
00:12:44,800 --> 00:12:49,899
The long night stretches on, without a guiding lamp...

230
00:12:50,400 --> 00:12:55,366
A lone wild goose cries in sorrow, having lost its kin...

231
00:12:55,800 --> 00:12:58,066
The spirit cultivator has passed.

232
00:12:58,567 --> 00:13:00,599
His soul has returned to the heavens.

233
00:13:01,300 --> 00:13:02,899
We inherit your final wish

234
00:13:03,500 --> 00:13:06,066
and guard this cherished land.

235
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:07,832
Heroic soul...

236
00:13:07,833 --> 00:13:09,299
Send Uncle Lei on his final journey.

237
00:13:09,567 --> 00:13:09,999
Return...

238
00:13:10,033 --> 00:13:10,399
Return...

239
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:10,766
Return...

240
00:13:10,767 --> 00:13:11,499
Return...

241
00:13:14,367 --> 00:13:15,966
The living are but passing travelers.

242
00:13:16,367 --> 00:13:18,066
The dead are those returning home.

243
00:13:18,500 --> 00:13:20,066
Heaven and earth are one fleeting inn,

244
00:13:20,400 --> 00:13:22,099
sharing the same eternal sorrow of dust.

245
00:13:25,400 --> 00:13:28,532
Heroic soul, return...

246
00:13:57,233 --> 00:13:58,233
Bro, look!

247
00:14:26,833 --> 00:14:27,833
Wait!

248
00:14:42,233 --> 00:14:43,233
Clear the way!

249
00:14:54,567 --> 00:14:55,567
Sister Ling'er.

250
00:14:55,600 --> 00:14:56,600
Take care.

251
00:14:57,233 --> 00:14:58,233
Take care.

252
00:14:59,233 --> 00:15:00,233
I was once a useless Phase-less person

253
00:15:00,567 --> 00:15:01,866
who only wanted to carry coffins for a living

254
00:15:02,233 --> 00:15:03,466
and cure my sister's strange illness.

255
00:15:04,467 --> 00:15:05,467
I never expected

256
00:15:05,767 --> 00:15:06,899
to be exiled to the Great Wilderness.

257
00:15:08,033 --> 00:15:09,266
Having witnessed life under the evil mist,

258
00:15:09,333 --> 00:15:10,333
where lives are worth less than ants,

259
00:15:11,100 --> 00:15:12,166
I made a great vow:

260
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:13,732
to save the people of the Great Wilderness.

261
00:15:15,600 --> 00:15:16,966
Now the evil mist has vanished,

262
00:15:17,433 --> 00:15:18,433
and the people live in peace.

263
00:15:19,800 --> 00:15:20,932
All my wishes have been fulfilled.

264
00:15:22,233 --> 00:15:23,233
This journey was not in vain.

265
00:15:25,193 --> 00:15:30,653
["The journey through the martial world is long, with towering mountains and endless rivers."]

266
00:15:30,915 --> 00:15:33,904
[Great Wilderness City: “The Great Wilderness is vast and boundless, yet it first wins hearts.”Ding Xiaoming was exiled to the Great Wilderness. The people there lived like grass, yet he was willing to risk his life to save them. Under the oppression of the monstrous beasts, countless lives suffered; after driving the beasts away, destiny entrusted him with the mission of rebuilding the Great Wilderness.
Starting from Leipo Village, he joined forces with Wu Xuan Sect, the foremost sect of the Great Wilderness, to establish a city—Great Wilderness City—providing a haven for displaced refugees and bringing them stability and safety. He also gathered the remaining beast tides and organized them into a powerful force, ensuring that no new threats would arise. After several years, they built a grand city housing one-third of the Great Wilderness population—Great Wilderness City—where the people now live and work in peace and contentment.]

267
00:15:33,928 --> 00:16:07,328
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

